aboutBlock.title: What you need to know, before you ask.

featuredSessions.description: Women Techmakers Moscow is hosting a global event series to celebrate the 2020 International Women’s Day. This will be a day-long conference, geared towards increasing visibility, community and resources for women in technology. The event will feature tech talks and ones on soft skills as well, hands on workshops, networking opportunities and more. And in true Google fashion, there will be plenty of food and excitement!

galleryBlock.title: First Women Techmakers Meetup Highlights
galleryBlock.description: Women Techmakers is an international program for women powered by Google. For women, who work for or interested in IT. The main goal is to help women to find themselves in this sphere, to give all necessary resources and knowledge and to create place for experience exchange.

blocks.title: Venue
blocks.description: International Women’s Day 2020 in Moscow will be held in the conference centre Newsroom. It is 400 sq. m. of a creative and comfortable space for business events with the latest communication and presentation tools, and technologies. Newsroom conference center is located within 3 minutes walking distance from "Kutuzovskaya" metro station and 10 minutes walking distance from "Park Pobedy" metro station.
